    Once upon a time.in a forest their lived a monkey who resided on a jamun tree. which was on the bank or river.
    In the same forest. their lived a crocodile and her wife. one doy the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree .the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruit. the crocodile came back the next day for more fruit, as he loved them .
    as day passed by the crocodile and monkey become good friend .
